      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:2:1:38:2",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ ( عليه السلام ) إِنَّ أَفْضَلَ الْعِبَادَةِ عِفَّةُ الْبَطْنِ وَ الْفَرْجِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Hanan Bin Sadeyr, from his father who said, ",
          "‘Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The most superior worship is the chastity of the belly and the private part’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from Muhammad ibn Isma’il from Hanan ibn Sadir from his father who has said the following: “Abu Ja’far (a.s.) has said, ‘The best worship is to be chaste in the matters of stomach and genital organs.’” "
        ]
      }
    }
